# Project Status

## Mission

Build free, genuinely useful tools for AI developers to validate demand, grow an email list, and help people.

## Success Metrics

- **Primary:** Someone reaches out saying "thank you"
- **Secondary:** Email subscriber growth (target: 500 in 3 months)
- **Tertiary:** Organic search traffic to tools

## Constraints

- Solo developer — limited maintenance bandwidth
- $0-20/month budget — free tiers (Render, Mailchimp)
- Tools run themselves — no manual maintenance required
- No user accounts — tools are free and anonymous

