- **Share URLs:** Always point to ai-buzz.com (never Render URLs)

## What "Done" Looks Like

For each tool:

1. API endpoints deployed on Render
2. Widget HTML created (self-contained)
3. Widget embedded on WordPress page via Bricks
4. Email capture working with correct Mailchimp tags
5. GA4 events firing for key actions
6. Share URL points to ai-buzz.com
7. Works on mobile (375px)
8. Handles API cold starts gracefully

## Known Issues / Tech Debt

- Render free tier cold starts (10-30s) — widgets handle gracefully
- No CI/CD pipeline yet (manual `pytest` for now)
